WEBVTT

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:32.390
Well, good evening, family. Thank you

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:34.950
for joining us again today. We're going

00:01:34.960 --> 00:01:36.870
to pray tonight; we have a lot to pray

00:01:36.880 --> 00:01:41.590
about all day today. I've had great

00:01:41.600 --> 00:01:43.990
urgency for what I'm seeing in the

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:47.109
spirit based on what we saw last night. If

00:01:47.119 --> 00:01:49.109
anybody was with us last night—and I

00:01:49.119 --> 00:01:50.870
know we're doing a lot of back-to-back

00:01:50.880 --> 00:01:52.469
videos, and I know there's a lot of you that

00:01:52.479 --> 00:01:54.950
don't have time to pray through all those videos

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:56.550
because it takes a lot of your

00:01:56.560 --> 00:01:57.830
day with families and

00:01:57.830 --> 00:01:57.840
things—I'll

00:01:57.840 --> 00:02:00.709
give you a little recap

00:02:00.719 --> 00:02:03.429
of what we prayed over and what the Lord

00:02:03.439 --> 00:02:08.150
showed us in the spirit.

00:02:08.160 --> 00:02:10.630
We give all the

00:02:10.640 --> 00:02:13.110
glory to God. Brandon

00:02:13.120 --> 00:02:14.790
is not able to do any of this on his

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:17.990
own. Everything that I believe the Lord

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:19.910
is showing me will prove to be

00:02:19.920 --> 00:02:22.150
accurate in the future, as you'll see

00:02:22.160 --> 00:02:24.309
in the news. But we don't pray the news;

00:02:24.319 --> 00:02:27.430
we pray ahead of time. We're

00:02:27.440 --> 00:02:31.350
watchmen; we see in advance. And

00:02:31.360 --> 00:02:34.470
for what we see, it's coming to pass. It

00:02:34.480 --> 00:02:36.710
looks like it for those who are

00:02:36.720 --> 00:02:38.790
part of my prayer team. I want to

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:41.750
call you all my elite prayer team.

00:02:41.760 --> 00:02:43.750
We have the best of the best

00:02:43.760 --> 00:02:46.390
prayer warriors. The Lord said, 'I've

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:49.350
assembled the best prayer warriors of

00:02:49.360 --> 00:02:53.430
this generation on your prayer team, and

00:02:53.440 --> 00:02:56.150
you all will pray and change things

00:02:56.160 --> 00:02:58.550
through prayer.'I believe with

00:02:58.560 --> 00:03:01.270
all my heart that word is coming to

00:03:01.280 --> 00:03:05.430
pass. There is a very strong core of

00:03:05.440 --> 00:03:07.430
you—125,000—that

00:03:07.440 --> 00:03:10.949
watch and pray, and that's

00:03:10.959 --> 00:03:12.869
just through this platform alone. We

00:03:12.879 --> 00:03:18.710
have a real solid 125,000 people who

00:03:18.710 --> 00:03:18.720
join

00:03:18.720 --> 00:03:20.710
almost every video and pray

00:03:20.720 --> 00:03:23.110
with us. We're so thankful for every

00:03:23.120 --> 00:03:25.430
single one of you who comes out. I would

00:03:25.440 --> 00:03:29.030
say we have a great group of

00:03:29.040 --> 00:03:31.910
intercessors, and I'm so thankful for

00:03:31.920 --> 00:03:33.030
every single one of you. We're going

00:03:33.040 --> 00:03:36.149
to go over what the Lord has shown us

00:03:36.159 --> 00:03:40.149
over the last video.

00:03:40.159 --> 00:03:42.229
Help me to remember everything

00:03:42.239 --> 00:03:44.949
because He showed us a lot,

00:03:44.959 --> 00:03:47.430
and He has my notes. First

00:03:47.440 --> 00:03:50.470
off, I saw something

00:03:50.480 --> 00:03:53.270
concerning Cuba. I saw

00:03:53.280 --> 00:03:58.070
a

00:03:58.080 --> 00:04:01.750
beautiful home,

00:04:01.750 --> 00:04:01.760
white-looking,

00:04:01.760 --> 00:04:05.270
with some kind of

00:04:05.270 --> 00:04:05.280
stucco

00:04:05.280 --> 00:04:07.270
roofs and clay shingles.

00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:09.750
It didn't

00:04:09.760 --> 00:04:11.750
look like

00:04:11.750 --> 00:04:11.760
modern-day

00:04:11.760 --> 00:04:13.910
asphalt shingles; these

00:04:17.440 --> 00:04:19.749
looked like clay shingles on a mansion

00:04:19.759 --> 00:04:21.670
in Cuba.

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:25.749
Underneath this mansion were tunnels

00:04:25.749 --> 00:04:25.759
and

00:04:25.759 --> 00:04:29.430
passageways that went in all

00:04:29.440 --> 00:04:31.990
different directions

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:40.230
to a bunker.

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:42.469
There was an escape route to a

00:04:42.479 --> 00:04:45.430
bunker inside the side of a

00:04:45.440 --> 00:04:48.230
mountain,

00:04:48.230 --> 00:04:48.240
where

00:04:48.240 --> 00:04:50.710
tunnels led to a place with

00:04:50.710 --> 00:04:50.720
an

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:54.070
escape route for a

00:04:54.080 --> 00:04:58.310
really nice boat. Then I saw a

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:00.070
helicopter

00:05:04.320 --> 00:05:06.950
take off from the top

00:05:06.950 --> 00:05:06.960
of the mountain.

00:05:06.960 --> 00:05:08.870
Everything the Lord was showing me

00:05:08.880 --> 00:05:12.150
was concerning the gray-headed man,

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:15.703
the leader of Cuba,

00:05:16.710 --> 00:05:16.720
Miguel

00:05:17.919 --> 00:05:19.189
Díaz-Canel.

00:05:21.919 --> 00:05:24.390
The Lord said again

00:05:24.400 --> 00:05:28.070
that He was going to get rid of

00:05:28.080 --> 00:05:30.550
the Castro

00:05:30.550 --> 00:05:30.560
name—the

00:05:30.560 --> 00:05:33.590
Castros, all of them—and that

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:35.510
there would basically be a bloodline cleansing

00:05:35.520 --> 00:05:38.469
of dictatorship out of that

00:05:38.479 --> 00:05:39.830
land.

00:05:39.840 --> 00:05:43.189
The Lord showed me again

00:05:43.199 --> 00:05:46.950
trade with Cuba coming with the United

00:05:46.960 --> 00:05:49.350
States of America.

00:05:52.240 --> 00:05:55.749
It will be like a state

00:05:55.759 --> 00:05:59.670
where Cuba and America will be friends

00:05:59.680 --> 00:06:02.550
with new leadership that will come about

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:06.790
with Marco Rubio.

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:11.350
I saw Rubio establishing a great Cuba

00:06:11.360 --> 00:06:13.990
in the days ahead that will bring

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:18.790
prosperity and economic stability

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:24.870
with a tourist industry. I saw

00:06:24.880 --> 00:06:28.629
resorts opening up on the water

00:06:28.629 --> 00:06:28.639
and

00:06:28.639 --> 00:06:31.670
great hotel chains from America going

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:35.029
into Cuba, bringing hotels and

00:06:35.039 --> 00:06:38.390
resorts for holiday travel.

00:06:41.520 --> 00:06:46.150
I saw the cigar industry—though I

00:06:46.160 --> 00:06:47.830
don't believe in smoking, this is

00:06:47.840 --> 00:06:53.670
what I saw—with golden band cigars

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:56.574
being traded around the world

00:06:56.574 --> 00:06:56.584
and

00:06:56.584 --> 00:06:59.029
into America; it was

00:06:59.039 --> 00:07:01.110
big business.

00:07:01.120 --> 00:07:02.710
On the other side of the

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:04.790
island, facing Jamaica, I saw a plant

00:07:09.830 --> 00:07:09.840
or

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:19.189
big business

00:07:19.189 --> 00:07:19.199
being

00:07:19.199 --> 00:07:21.670
established.

00:07:21.680 --> 00:07:25.270
I saw American-made

00:07:25.270 --> 00:07:25.280
cars—Ford,

00:07:25.280 --> 00:07:30.550
GMC, and Chevrolet—going over to

00:07:30.560 --> 00:07:32.150
Cuba.

00:07:32.160 --> 00:07:35.029
I

00:07:35.039 --> 00:07:36.950
don't know if they have a factory there

00:07:36.950 --> 00:07:36.960
or

00:07:36.960 --> 00:07:38.070
if they're just

00:07:38.070 --> 00:07:38.080
buying

00:07:38.080 --> 00:07:39.830
our automobiles, but

00:07:39.830 --> 00:07:39.840
I

00:07:39.840 --> 00:07:44.309
saw F-150 trucks, Ford,

00:07:44.319 --> 00:07:47.830
and GMC trucks all going to Cuba in the

00:07:47.840 --> 00:07:51.029
days ahead, with people

00:07:51.039 --> 00:07:55.510
driving new and used trucks.

00:07:55.520 --> 00:07:59.510
I saw economic growth

00:07:59.510 --> 00:07:59.520
and

00:07:59.520 --> 00:08:03.589
stability coming to Cuba again. But

00:08:03.599 --> 00:08:06.869
the Lord said, 'You must pray for what's

00:08:06.879 --> 00:08:09.110
about to happen in the near

00:08:09.110 --> 00:08:09.120
future.'I'm

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:10.550
not going to give time frames

00:08:10.560 --> 00:08:13.110
because the Lord told me this

00:08:13.120 --> 00:08:21.909
is very soon.

00:08:21.919 --> 00:08:26.629
I saw all this stuff coming

00:08:26.639 --> 00:08:28.390
specifically

00:08:28.400 --> 00:08:31.189
in

00:08:31.199 --> 00:08:35.029
the darkness. We must

00:08:35.039 --> 00:08:38.709
pray tonight for a hedge of protection

00:08:38.719 --> 00:08:43.909
around people.

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:51.990
Then the vision switched to Iran.

00:08:54.560 --> 00:08:56.550
This was very serious

00:08:56.550 --> 00:08:56.560
and

00:08:56.560 --> 00:08:59.509
heavy.

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:03.829
There were things I was hearing

00:09:03.839 --> 00:09:06.470
because I was caught up, and I could

00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:08.550
hear the conversation

00:09:08.560 --> 00:09:11.829
taking place with the man appointed to

00:09:11.829 --> 00:09:11.839
the Ayatollah

00:09:11.839 --> 00:09:14.150
committee today,

00:09:14.160 --> 00:09:16.710
the leader of

00:09:16.720 --> 00:09:20.389
Iran. I heard him underground talking to

00:09:20.399 --> 00:09:23.590
a man with a white beard and a white

00:09:23.600 --> 00:09:27.030
turban.

00:09:27.040 --> 00:09:30.389
He was

00:09:30.399 --> 00:09:32.949
asking this elder,

00:09:43.760 --> 00:09:47.750
'Is it time to

00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:53.030
go ahead with phase

00:09:53.030 --> 00:09:53.040
two?'I

00:09:53.040 --> 00:09:56.150
saw massive

00:09:58.080 --> 00:10:01.190
missiles and underground

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:04.710
military installations with

00:10:04.710 --> 00:10:04.720
biological

00:10:04.720 --> 00:10:08.230
weapons of mass destruction.

00:10:08.240 --> 00:10:12.230
I

00:10:12.240 --> 00:10:14.310
believe

00:10:14.320 --> 00:10:19.670
I saw things from Saddam in

00:10:19.670 --> 00:10:19.680
Iraq

00:10:19.680 --> 00:10:21.829
from

00:10:21.839 --> 00:10:25.590
when we went

00:10:25.600 --> 00:10:27.030
after them for weapons of mass

00:10:27.040 --> 00:10:31.110
destruction in 2000.

00:10:31.120 --> 00:10:36.150
There was

00:10:36.150 --> 00:10:36.160
chemical warfare

00:10:36.160 --> 00:10:39.430
that would make your

00:10:39.440 --> 00:10:43.590
skin

00:10:43.600 --> 00:10:47.110
melt off your body with massive boils,

00:10:47.120 --> 00:10:49.590
and

00:10:49.600 --> 00:10:52.310
I saw people convulse to the point

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:54.790
that their

00:10:57.839 --> 00:10:59.910
spines

00:11:01.920 --> 00:11:05.509
snapped.

00:11:08.320 --> 00:11:10.150
I'm just telling you what I saw in the

00:11:10.160 --> 00:11:11.670
vision.

00:11:11.680 --> 00:11:15.750
I saw that it was used up toward

00:11:15.750 --> 00:11:15.760
the

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:20.470
Damascus area and that

00:11:20.470 --> 00:11:20.480
part of

00:11:20.480 --> 00:11:22.630
Israel.

00:11:25.440 --> 00:11:28.630
It was an attack worse than October

00:11:28.640 --> 00:11:33.190
7th of four years ago.

00:11:33.200 --> 00:11:36.949
This was an attack plan.

00:11:36.959 --> 00:11:41.110
He asked, 'Do the prophecies line up? Are we

00:11:41.120 --> 00:11:43.910
really

00:11:46.720 --> 00:11:49.269
there?'The

00:11:50.959 --> 00:11:53.910
Lord allowed me to

00:11:53.910 --> 00:11:53.920
understand

00:11:53.920 --> 00:11:57.030
him

00:11:57.030 --> 00:11:57.040
asking,

00:11:57.040 --> 00:12:00.069
'Is it really time

00:12:00.079 --> 00:12:03.110
for the Mahdi

00:12:03.110 --> 00:12:03.120
to come?'They

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:06.710
were discussing the Quran

00:12:06.720 --> 00:12:08.949
and

00:12:08.959 --> 00:12:12.629
Muslim prophetic words,

00:12:12.639 --> 00:12:15.910
looking for the sign of

00:12:15.920 --> 00:12:18.870
their savior,

00:12:18.870 --> 00:12:18.880
the

00:12:18.880 --> 00:12:22.310
Mahdi.

00:12:22.320 --> 00:12:26.230
I heard them discussing how to bring forth

00:12:26.240 --> 00:12:28.629
this

00:12:28.639 --> 00:12:31.269
false god, whom we believe is the

00:12:31.279 --> 00:12:33.190
Antichrist.

00:12:33.200 --> 00:12:34.790
Remember,

00:12:34.800 --> 00:12:39.590
I told you when the Mahdi comes, it's

00:12:39.600 --> 00:12:42.550
on Fridays that you're made to worship

00:12:42.560 --> 00:12:44.550
during the Tribulation,

00:12:44.550 --> 00:12:44.560
wearing

00:12:44.560 --> 00:12:48.310
white clothes and using rugs. Everyone around

00:12:48.310 --> 00:12:48.320
the world

00:12:48.320 --> 00:12:51.110
will be required to

00:12:51.120 --> 00:12:54.150
look at the man on the screen;

00:12:54.160 --> 00:12:57.269
he will be the Antichrist. I'm telling

00:12:57.279 --> 00:13:01.509
you, I've seen it. On July 6,

00:13:01.509 --> 00:13:01.519
2014,

00:13:01.519 --> 00:13:03.829
I was taken out of my body, and the

00:13:03.839 --> 00:13:06.470
Lord took me to the Tribulation.

00:13:06.470 --> 00:13:06.480
Whether

00:13:06.480 --> 00:13:07.910
you believe that or

00:13:07.910 --> 00:13:07.920
not,

00:13:07.920 --> 00:13:09.430
I'm telling you what

00:13:09.430 --> 00:13:09.440
is

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:13.204
coming.

00:13:13.214 --> 00:13:13.750
People

00:13:13.760 --> 00:13:16.949
were on mats on Fridays, and

00:13:16.949 --> 00:13:16.959
everyone

00:13:16.959 --> 00:13:19.670
was required to worship

00:13:19.670 --> 00:13:19.680
the

00:13:19.680 --> 00:13:24.150
image of this man on a screen

00:13:24.160 --> 00:13:27.590
in major towns. It's at the Vatican. It

00:13:27.600 --> 00:13:29.670
will be all over the place. Everyone

00:13:29.680 --> 00:13:31.670
will go to the Vatican and they will

00:13:31.680 --> 00:13:34.389
worship the Antichrist there one day. I

00:13:34.399 --> 00:13:37.269
saw it. It will be in France. It will

00:13:37.279 --> 00:13:39.670
be in America, in Washington. It will be

00:13:39.680 --> 00:13:41.030
all over the place. There will be

00:13:41.040 --> 00:13:43.269
screens and everybody will be required

00:13:43.279 --> 00:13:45.829
to worship somebody.

00:13:45.839 --> 00:13:50.069
If you do not, they take your head off.

00:13:50.079 --> 00:13:53.350
I'm telling you that as I was listening

00:13:53.360 --> 00:13:56.389
to this man talk underground in a

00:13:56.399 --> 00:13:58.069
bunker,

00:13:58.079 --> 00:14:00.389
I could see missiles and things around

00:14:00.399 --> 00:14:02.470
him.

00:14:02.480 --> 00:14:05.189
He was talking about some kind of weapon

00:14:05.199 --> 00:14:06.949
they had that they believe

00:14:06.959 --> 00:14:10.949
nobody else had.

00:14:10.959 --> 00:14:14.710
They were talking about a weapon

00:14:14.720 --> 00:14:18.790
they have that nobody knows they have.

00:14:18.800 --> 00:14:21.590
It was

00:14:21.600 --> 00:14:24.150
one thing.

00:14:24.160 --> 00:14:27.910
They had one thing and I believe this

00:14:27.920 --> 00:14:31.110
was a nuclear thing. This was something

00:14:31.120 --> 00:14:33.750
they've developed or they have

00:14:33.760 --> 00:14:37.110
received from someone else, but it was on

00:14:37.120 --> 00:14:41.030
a payload on a rocket

00:14:41.040 --> 00:14:45.030
and I saw him touching the rocket.

00:14:45.040 --> 00:14:47.910
He was talking about this massive

00:14:47.920 --> 00:14:50.550
thing. He was talking to the man with

00:14:50.560 --> 00:14:53.110
the white beard. They were under the

00:14:53.120 --> 00:14:55.509
ground and they were discussing biblical

00:14:55.509 --> 00:14:55.519
prophecy

00:14:55.519 --> 00:14:57.269
there. Now, I keep saying

00:14:57.279 --> 00:14:58.710
