00:14:58.710 --> 00:14:58.720
do—Quran

00:14:58.720 --> 00:15:03.430
prophecy, false god prophecy.

00:15:03.440 --> 00:15:05.350
And they were talking about this and

00:15:05.360 --> 00:15:08.550
they were saying, "Is it time to push

00:15:08.560 --> 00:15:12.230
the button? Is it time? Do you believe

00:15:12.240 --> 00:15:15.590
we're at the time for the Mahdi

00:15:15.590 --> 00:15:15.600
