00:15:35.839 --> 00:15:39.350
And they said, "We have to activate the

00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:43.750
cells in America. It's

00:15:43.750 --> 00:15:43.760
time."And

00:15:43.760 --> 00:15:46.389
they were discussing underground,

00:15:46.399 --> 00:15:48.629
these two men—the man that was

00:15:48.639 --> 00:15:52.150
pronounced to be the head of Iran today.

00:15:52.160 --> 00:15:55.990
I heard him say, "We must communicate to

00:15:56.000 --> 00:15:59.110
the terrorists, these

00:15:59.120 --> 00:16:03.350
cells in America, and activate them. Is

00:16:03.360 --> 00:16:05.590
it

00:16:05.590 --> 00:16:05.600
time?"And

00:16:05.600 --> 00:16:07.269
he was talking to the man with the

00:16:07.279 --> 00:16:11.430
white beard. I heard this. It was very

00:16:11.440 --> 00:16:13.670
detailed. I'm not telling you everything

00:16:13.680 --> 00:16:16.389
