00:16:16.399 --> 00:16:18.790
You need to know

00:16:18.800 --> 00:16:20.710
we're in a time like we've never seen

00:16:20.720 --> 00:16:24.230
before. The Lord said—and this is why

00:16:24.240 --> 00:16:28.310
the church has to rise up and pray like

00:16:28.320 --> 00:16:31.030
we've never prayed

00:16:31.030 --> 00:16:31.040
before—because

00:16:31.040 --> 00:16:33.670
we understand that Jesus Christ

00:16:33.680 --> 00:16:37.269
is coming and that our Jesus, our

00:16:37.279 --> 00:16:41.030
Savior, is coming for the bride. But the

00:16:41.040 --> 00:16:43.509
Lord said, "I'm coming back for a

